  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d89\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dda \u0d85\u0db4\u0dd2\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I have cancer: Biden says",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "\"We presented Dallas. We voted. He lost,\" former President Mahinda Rajapaksa said while answering the questions asked by journalists after the presidential vote in Parliament.",
        "After the end of the parliamentary session in which the president is elected, the former president said the following while answering the questions asked by the journalists while coming out of the chamber.",
        "Question: He was your eternal rival. In the end, you too must have voted for him.",
        "Answer:- We are waiting to see how it will happen. It would be good if there is a government that works for the people. We are waiting.",
        "Answer: - No such decision has been taken yet. I agree with the decisions taken by the party.",
        "Question :-The chairman of your party took a different decision and he supported Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma who ran from your party.",
        "Answer :- We presented Dallas. We voted. He lost. Someone has to win. Those who win win. Those who lose lose.",
        "Question: Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe is facing objection. It is said that this is not the right opinion.",
        "Answer: There is one opinion on the other. They say that it is the opinion of the people. We say it is not. There are both opinions on it."
      ],
